{"tid":83752,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老細偏心自己","createTime":"2017-01-17T03:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T05:46:08.000Z","uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46817c061cfbcb676cfe2523b5b8694b89a77817","tid":83752,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:54:40.000Z","msg":"自問乖乖女 做嘢聽教聽話<br />\n默默工作 不爭寵 同大多數同事都相處到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老細都好支持我<br />\n但愈來愈覺得老細偏心自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如一班人工作上有問題<br />\n我自問自己都有不足的地方 可以再做好啲 我亦都有當面認錯 但我老細係其他人面前勁撐我 搞到某啲同事覺得唔高興 同埋覺得我俾鍋人地咩 <br />\n但老細偏心 咪搞到好似人地錯 我無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦唔知點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連一個工作上無交往嘅秘書都不喜歡我 話我都唔係好靚啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (其實我都唔知有乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n請問我可以點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我只想大家一齊工作的開開心心"},{"pid":"da5a2823e5a53dcd5018ce5c8c004546b9a5dced","tid":83752,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"唔好幫老細吹咁多"},{"pid":"5f9e6dc411349ecd145e8ca21c2cc0c79bb2fabe","tid":83752,"uid":39508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:20:07.000Z","msg":"無辦法架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不招人妒是庸才<br />\n要人放下成見係好難<br />\n以後唯有做野小心d越唔搞到人越好<br />\n<br />\n不過有d老細明玩野借一派打一派<br />\n明明你做得唔係最好但都讚下你其實係俾說話其他人聽<br />\n點都幾時都低調就最好<br />\n不貪功 低調 少說話<br />\n有人要幫手就出力d咪亂托人手㬹"},{"pid":"5c3f5ede3f573b7f1ca2ef6b5a1bbd8a5a81d76b","tid":83752,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:46:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無辦法架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"